metadata.name: Lady of the Lake
metadata.description:
To get into the world of legends and fairy tales, I decided to make an animated picture. Light movements and beautiful music, will make you look closely at the mysterious mistress of the lake. Watch her breathing and how the wind quietly sways her curls. But I want to warn you, be careful, because she can enchant you with her beauty. 

Edition: 1/1
